{"tid":56491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你喺廢老，你嘅一日會點過？","createTime":"2016-12-27T09:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T10:01:27.000Z","uid":90,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb35e2245c6eceb38247efafb546a226dcc2e38","tid":56491,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"7:00-7:15起身刷牙<br />\n7:15-7:30喺屋企行陣<br />\n7:30-8:00換衫出門口，準備去最近嘅火車站<br />\n8:00-8:30用2蚊優惠搭地鐵同班後生爭位<br />\n8:30-9:00坐住關愛座望住班後生企<br />\n9:15-12:00去飲茶，同班老友記吹水<br />\n12:00-1:00行下商場，睇完唔買<br />\n1:00-2:00去公園散步+捉棋/睇人捉<br />\n2:00-4:00 去地盤睇人做嘢<br />\n4:00-5:00去m記攞杯水/買雪糕之後坐<br />\n5:00-6:00 行去地鐵站，又用兩蚊搭車<br />\n6:00-7:00 坐住關愛座，睇住你班友放工都冇得坐<br />\n7:00-8:00 返屋企食飯<br />\n8:00-9:30 睇電視<br />\n9:30-10:30 同個孫講日本仔好衰，乜乜之類，鳩吹自己有份打仗，分析歷史但其實乜都唔識<br />\n10:30-11:30去刷牙沖涼<br />\n11:30去瞓"},{"pid":"244ca373f145b6edb5994842f10735d4931efae0","tid":56491,"uid":31369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170bce7d1312ad63b991e77646d3c96d004d0220","tid":56491,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"7~8 起身+早餐<br />\n8~13 周圍行𥄫女<br />\n13~14午餐<br />\n14~19周圍行𥄫女<br />\n19~20 晚飯 <br />\n20~22 屋企樓下大堂𥄫女<br />\n22~8瞓教"},{"pid":"207aed657a509607bd12c5ea9309281259208616","tid":56491,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7~8 起身+早餐<br />\n8~13 周圍行𥄫女<br />\n13~14午餐<br />\n14~19周圍行𥄫女<br />\n19~20 晚飯 <br />\n20~22 屋企樓下大堂𥄫女<br />\n22~8瞓教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇咁多女𥄫？"},{"pid":"0bc85933949ce9e70ea3849748b9e204bc01d01e","tid":56491,"uid":20943,"like":0,"disl