n7:00-8:00 返屋企食飯<br />\n8:00-9:30 睇電視<br />\n9:30-10:30 同個孫講日本仔好衰，乜乜之類，鳩吹自己有份打仗，分析歷史但其實乜都唔識<br />\n10:30-11:30去刷牙沖涼<br />\n11:30去瞓</blockquote><br />\n重點好似去左坐住關愛座睇住人冇位坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2697b9b60c0214454c3a1df747d438f062a92e","tid":56491,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:42:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"01de0554f30e0ad07fae72fb5578db5de95ab187","tid":56491,"uid":16637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"仲有馬會門口呢？"},{"pid":"5a1c1f4a0ae830155deec3c8cb383cfc34bcd4d9","tid":56491,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"廿四小時坐喺瑪利諾門口"},{"pid":"22ea82a449f600ce17ec52a8d9a6330d179ddf78","tid":56491,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有馬會門口呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個啲係賭錢個堆啫<br />\n唔係個個都去"},{"pid":"031551b1ccfe0ce8728827971c5a350797e60bac","tid":56491,"uid":33916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1-2PM 緊撚係去食肆霸撚住係班廢青食飯個位啦<br />\n6-7PM 就搭地鐵? 你都ON9 今時今日廢青邊有咁早收工, 緊係1830~1945 搭車啦<br />\n<br />\n一睇就知你唔識玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早咗tim<br />\n巴打睇嚟高手</blockquote><br />\n坐唔倒個幾鐘車咁耐的話仲可以1930~ 2000 去各大連鎖快餐店<br />\n妹下妹下排隊買野食, 去到收銀先逐個餐問有乜野包乜野有冇特價<br />\n之後仲要響個袋度妹下妹下d 散銀, 最緊要要妹唔夠數再拎張100蚊出黎找<br />\n<br />\n最最最緊要係要簡條開得一個收銀既鋪頭去玩阻撚住班廢青買狗糧"},{"pid":"371a224997ae8069ea25400703b8096f5b27cd9d","tid":56491,"uid":26420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7defa09fb94db9f363f4f29c815c33f47e73d0","tid":56491,"uid":33916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"等唔倒1-2pm 咁晏食飯的話仲可以去銀行妹d 櫃員機<br />\n務求等你班廢青唔可以趁食飯果陣順手禁埋錢入支票etc."},{"pid":"4c5082e1455fd988d6c24d814063ba43e7df9498","tid":56491,"uid":24982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"仲有拎免費報紙呀"},{"pid":"6331483063d3f9f2eef6d9611382013cea972d80","tid":56491,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有拎免費報紙呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲好似執紙皮賣個啲先咁做多"}]}